@startuml
title Statechart diagram of Plane Lifecycle

[*] --> Order
Order --> Arrival
Arrival --> Preparation
Preparation --> Operations : condition and schedule or no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
Operations --> Maintenance : scheduled flights end or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced
Preparation --> OutOfService : unavailable for use or if no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
OutOfService --> [*] : permanently withdrawn from service
@enduml
